    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed in full transparency as a car in mint condition \u2014 buyers can feel confident they are looking at an exceptional example of a well-preserved, meticulously maintained automobile. The exterior is essentially flawless, with no visible scratches, dents, or paint imperfections; the finish retains a deep, factory-fresh shine throughout. The interior is equally impressive, showing virtually no signs of wear \u2014 the upholstery, dashboard, carpets, and all trim pieces look as though they have barely been used. All mechanical systems are in excellent working order, with no known issues; the engine runs smoothly, all electronics function perfectly, and the ride is tight and responsive. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has clearly been cared for with great attention and pride of ownership. Ideal for a buyer who wants a move-in-ready car with nothing to fix, replace, or worry about.",
